Finance
For information on financial support you can access whilst abroad, visit our financial assistance guidance.
Returning to the UK
When you return, you must follow the rules for entering the UK. There are currently no commercial options available to return to the UK from Namibia.
Help and support
If you need urgent consular assistance, you can contact the British High Commission on +264 61 274800
